nd_text_1:
What?
I thought you said you were having fun!
nd_text_2:
*sigh*
I was, sweetheart. The first 5 minutes I was, but this whole experience has gone dull.
nd_text_3: Maybe we shouldn't have accepted the invitation to come here.
nd_text_5: Not so long ago we got an invitation from a stranger to this... "party".
nd_text_7:
I think everyone here was tricked the same way.
I don't know how this was possible.
We don't even know how we got here.
I don't think we'll ever be able to go back.
